#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an8.15"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.15:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Mahāvagga "
msgstr "2. The Great Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an8.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Malasutta "
msgstr "15. Stains "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an8.15:1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhimāni, bhikkhave, malāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these eight stains. "

msgctxt "an8.15:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni aṭṭha? "
msgstr "What eight? "

msgctxt "an8.15:1.3"
msgid "Asajjhāyamalā, bhikkhave, mantā; "
msgstr "Not reciting is the stain of hymns. "

msgctxt "an8.15:1.4"
msgid "anuṭṭhānamalā, bhikkhave, gharā; "
msgstr "Neglect is the stain of houses. "

msgctxt "an8.15:1.5"
msgid "malaṃ, bhikkhave, vaṇṇassa kosajjaṃ; "
msgstr "Laziness is the stain of beauty. "

msgctxt "an8.15:1.6"
msgid "pamādo, bhikkhave, rakkhato malaṃ; "
msgstr "Negligence is a guard’s stain. "

msgctxt "an8.15:1.7"
msgid "malaṃ, bhikkhave, itthiyā duccaritaṃ; "
msgstr "Misconduct is a woman’s stain. "

msgctxt "an8.15:1.8"
msgid "maccheraṃ, bhikkhave, dadato malaṃ; "
msgstr "Stinginess is a giver’s stain. "

msgctxt "an8.15:1.9"
msgid "malā, bhikkhave, pāpakā akusalā dhammā asmiṃ loke paramhi ca; "
msgstr "Bad, unskillful qualities are a stain in this world and the next. "

#. VAR: tato → tato ca (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an8.15:1.10"
msgid "tato, bhikkhave, malā malataraṃ avijjā paramaṃ malaṃ. "
msgstr "Worse than any of these is ignorance, the worst stain of all. "

msgctxt "an8.15:1.11"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha malānīti. "
msgstr "These are the eight stains. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an8.15:2.1"
msgid "Asajjhāyamalā mantā, "
msgstr "Hymns get stained when they’re not recited. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.15:2.2"
msgid "anuṭṭhānamalā gharā; "
msgstr "The stain of houses is neglect. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.15:2.3"
msgid "Malaṃ vaṇṇassa kosajjaṃ, "
msgstr "Laziness is the stain of beauty. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.15:2.4"
msgid "pamādo rakkhato malaṃ. "
msgstr "A guard’s stain is negligence. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an8.15:3.1"
msgid "Malitthiyā duccaritaṃ, "
msgstr "Misconduct is a woman’s stain. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.15:3.2"
msgid "maccheraṃ dadato malaṃ; "
msgstr "A giver’s stain is stinginess. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.15:3.3"
msgid "Malā ve pāpakā dhammā, "
msgstr "Bad qualities are a stain "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.15:3.4"
msgid "asmiṃ loke paramhi ca; "
msgstr "in this world and the next. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.15:3.5"
msgid "Tato malā malataraṃ, "
msgstr "But a worse stain than these "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an8.15:3.6"
msgid "avijjā paramaṃ malan”ti. "
msgstr "is ignorance, the worst of stains.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.15:3.7"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
